did.unittitle: Commencement programs, commencement invitations, and a diploma

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Includes commencement programs for 1938, 1945, 1946, 1958, and 1961; commencement exercises invitations, 1946 and 1961 and associated name cards (for Kent P. Hollingsworth, 1946, and Karl Merrill Eldridge, 1961); and diploma for Ellen Lee Clark, 1961.
